      "message": "if we don\u0027t accept a result id from the client, then the client may have problems inserting multiple results for the same (invocation_id, test_id) in the same request. This is a fairly typical case, while multiple exonerations for the same (invocation_id, test_id) is very atypical (because one is enough to exonerate).\n\nWDYT about making ResultId in Spanner a string \"{short_request_id_hash}:{result_id}\"? if the client did not provide request_id, then generate something random yourself. When reading ResultID column, we\u0027d strip the hash.\n\nseparate CL is fine",
